summary: Just a blind version of Jenassa with beautiful hair :)
descriptionHtml:
---------------------------------------------------------
		Blind Jenassa
		 by Tvirus81
---------------------------------------------------------

[Version]

1.0

[Description]

First of all, sorry my bad english. This is my first mod.
Just a blind version of Jenassa with beautiful hair.

[Required Files]
	
ApachiiSkyHair - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168

[Installation]

Extract the content of the zip file in your data folder.

[Uninstallation]

Delete "BlindJenassa.esp"
Delete \Data\Textures\actors\character\FaceGenData\FaceTint\Skyrim.esm\000B9982.dds
Delete \Data\Meshes\actors\character\FaceGenData\FaceGeom\Skyrim.esm\000B9982.nif

[Compatabilities]

Not compatible with other mods which change Jenassa's appearance.


[Credits]

Apachii - ApachiiSkyHair - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168


[Contact]

Tvirus81

A special thanks to Magistrate for helping me with my first mod :)
